<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="16">Chart Axis</Paragraph><Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14">The following list includes features that illustrate the various customization options for chart axes.</Paragraph>

<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"><Bold>ChartAxis Elements Configuration Demo</Bold>-Demonstrates the customization of chart axis properties such as <Bold>Line Stroke</Bold>, <Bold>Opposed Position</Bold>,<Bold>Origin</Bold>, <Bold>Invert</Bold>,<Bold>Auto-Set Range</Bold>,<Bold>Label Format</Bold>, <Bold>Label Rotation</Bold>, <Bold>Label Font Size</Bold>, <Bold>Font Family</Bold><Bold>Interval</Bold> and <Bold>Gridline</Bold></Paragraph>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Calibri" FontSize="14"><Bold>AxisLabels Positioning Demo</Bold>-Illustrates the use of chart axis properties such as header position, label height, label width, label horizontal alignment, label vertical alignment, labels prefix, labels postfix, and edge labels drawing mode which portrays the improvement in the chart axis.</Paragraph>
